From: Peng Li <lipeng321@huawei.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Aug 2021 14:06:37 +0800
Subject: net: hns3: reconstruct function hns3_self_test
Patch-mainline: v5.15-rc1
Git-commit: 4c8dab1c709c5a715bce14efdb8f4e889d86aa04
